trans-unit.source: Provides a type converter for <xref href="System.Web.UI.DataBindingCollection"></xref> objects.
trans-unit.target: Gir et typen konverteringsprogram for <xref href="System.Web.UI.DataBindingCollection"> </xref> objekter.

trans-unit.source: This type converter calls the base <xref:System.ComponentModel.TypeConverter.ConvertTo%2A?displayProperty=fullName> method for all destination types except <xref:System.String>, for which an empty string ("") is returned.
trans-unit.target: Denne typen konverteringsprogram kaller grunntallet <xref:System.ComponentModel.TypeConverter.ConvertTo%2A?displayProperty=fullName>metode for alle mål typer unntatt <xref:System.String>, som en tom streng (""), returneres.</xref:System.String> </xref:System.ComponentModel.TypeConverter.ConvertTo%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: Initializes an instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.DataBindingCollectionConverter"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en forekomst av den <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.DataBindingCollectionConverter"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: Converts a data binding collection to the specified type.
trans-unit.target: Konverterer en samling for binding av data til den angitte typen.

trans-unit.source: This method returns an empty string if the `destinationType` parameter is of type <xref:System.String>.
trans-unit.target: Denne metoden returnerer en tom streng hvis den `destinationType` parameteren er av typen <xref:System.String>.</xref:System.String>

trans-unit.source: Otherwise this method calls the <xref:System.ComponentModel.TypeConverter.ConvertTo%2A> method of the base <xref:System.ComponentModel.TypeConverter> class.
trans-unit.target: Hvis kaller denne metoden <xref:System.ComponentModel.TypeConverter.ConvertTo%2A>-metoden til base <xref:System.ComponentModel.TypeConverter>klasse.</xref:System.ComponentModel.TypeConverter> </xref:System.ComponentModel.TypeConverter.ConvertTo%2A>

trans-unit.source: An <xref href="System.ComponentModel.ITypeDescriptorContext"></xref> that indicates the component or control to which the data binding collection belongs.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.ComponentModel.ITypeDescriptorContext"> </xref> som angir komponenten eller kontrollen bindingen datainnsamlingen tilhører.

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Globalization.CultureInfo> that can be used to provide additional culture information.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.Globalization.CultureInfo>som kan brukes til å angi flere kulturinformasjon.</xref:System.Globalization.CultureInfo>

trans-unit.source: The object produced by the type conversion.
trans-unit.target: Objektet som ble produsert av typen konverteringen.

trans-unit.source: If the destinationType parameter is of type , this method returns an empty string ("").
trans-unit.target: Hvis den destinationType parameteren er av typen , returneres en tom streng ("").
